@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
    ViewBag.Message = "Welcome to FreshMart - Your Trusted Online Grocery Store!";
}
<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h2 id="title">@ViewBag.Title</h2>
    <h4>@ViewBag.Message</h4>

    <p>
        FreshMart is a sample ASP.NET MVC web application built to demonstrate modern web development best practices using the Microsoft technology stack.
        The app allows customers to browse, search, and purchase fresh groceries online with a user-friendly interface.
    </p>

    <p>
        This project was developed by <strong>Kundan Patil</strong>, a passionate <strong>.NET Full Stack Developer</strong> with 3+ years of experience in designing and developing robust, scalable web applications using technologies like:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>C#, ASP.NET MVC, Entity Framework, and SQL Server</li>
        <li>Bootstrap, jQuery, and AJAX for responsive UI</li>
        <li>Identity for user authentication</li>
        <li>Real-world features like cart, checkout, order history, ratings, and more</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        Whether you're a recruiter, fellow developer, or a curious learner, this project showcases hands-on skills in software engineering, database design, and clean UI development.
        Feel free to check out other projects or connect with me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kundanpatil" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>
</main>
